<title>USA: United Asset to buy Pacific Financial.</title>
<headline>United Asset to buy Pacific Financial.</headline>
<dateline>BOSTON 1997-03-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>United Asset Management Corp said on Thursday that it has agreed to acquire Pacific Financial Research Inc, a manager of equity and balanced portfolios with $4.2 billion in assets.</p>
<p>Terms of the deal were not disclosed.</p>
<p>The deal would be accounted for as a purchase and is expected to close in May 1997, United Asset Management said.</p>
<p>All 25 of Pacific Financial's employees will retain their current positions after the deal is completed, United Asset said.</p>
